   Hii <%= @ud.name %> your booking request has been sent to Admin. Wait till it is confirmed.
  <strong><p>Booking Panding....</p></strong>
<%else%>  
  Congratulation <%= @ud.name %> Parking slot successfully booked.You can park your car.
  <ul>
    <% m= @ud.out_time %>
    <% n= @ud.in_time %>
    <li><strong>Slot Id: <strong><%= @ud.slot_id %></li>
